      "content": "thanks. those are okay. i'm a bit worried though, some of my regular customers have been complaining about \"woke\" stuff lately and saying DEI is just corporate pandering. can u make the captions sound less like a political statement and maybe more like it's just about being a nice business? like, focus on the \"welcoming\" part without using all the buzzwords like 'equity' or 'inclusion' if possible?",
